                <p ALIGN="LEFT">
                    Below are preliminary entrants for the 2025 Lottery (December 7, 2024).
                    The Ticket Count refers to the fact that lottery applicants receive
                    additional chances in the drawing for each failure to gain entry in a
                    prior year at 2^(n-1) where n is the number of years entering the lottery.
                </p>

                <P ALIGN="LEFT"><B>These are preliminary ticket counts.</B>
